Uber Pro is a rewards program that recognizes outstanding drivers, to help you reach your goals—on and off the road.
With Uber Pro, you have the opportunity to unlock new rewards as you reach higher status. Check your app to see what’s available in your area.
Keep more money in your pocket
Depending on your Uber Pro status and location, enjoy priority pickups at airports, gas savings with the Uber Debit Card,¹ and more.
With Uber Pro, you can get access to rewards such as roadside assistance, up to 25% off car maintenance,² and more.
More opportunities for you and your family
views.signature: [class]android.view.View[resource_id]None[text]More opportunities for you and your family[enabled,,]

views.text: Qualifying drivers receive 100% tuition coverage at ASU online that can be used by the driver or transferred to an eligible family member.³ Take classes toward a degree or certificates that can help you or your loved one move toward opportunity.
Drive with Uber to earn points. Some trips may earn you more points than others. See more details in the Driver app.
In addition to earning points, you must maintain certain ratings to earn Gold, Platinum, and Diamond rewards. The requirements vary by region. Please check the Driver app for more information.
The higher the status you earn, the more rewards you unlock. Your status is determined based on your points and quality ratings over a fixed 3-month period.
Trips completed during select hours each day earn extra points. Check the Driver app to see when you can earn points faster.
Quality service to riders unlocks more rewards
views.signature: [class]android.view.View[resource_id]None[text]Quality service to riders unlocks more rewards[enabled,,]

views.text: Rewards are given based on how you use the Driver app. To unlock Gold, Platinum, and Diamond status and continue receiving rewards, you must earn points and maintain certain ratings. To get more information, tap the menu icon in the Driver app, then tap Uber Pro and the right arrow near the top of the screen.
Earn points and enjoy rewards during fixed 3-month periods
You earn points during fixed 3-month periods. Points reset after each period.

When you earn enough points to unlock the next status of rewards, you start enjoying your new rewards right away. Keep your rating high and cancellation rate low to continue enjoying rewards until the end of the next 3-month period.
